LEARNING (es2)

per k=5:

parliament
soccer
championship
government
italian

P(c1)=(Wc1/|Voc|)=3/5=0.6
P(c2)=(Wc2/|Voc|)=3/5=0.6

p(w|c)= p(parliament|sport)= (d(w,c) + Wc)/d(c)+|Voc|= (0+3)/(3+5)= 0.375
p(w|c)= p(parliament|politics)= (d(w,c) + Wc)/d(c)+|Voc|= (2+3)/(3+5)= 0.625

p(w|c)= p(soccer|sport)= (d(w,c) + Wc)/d(c)+|Voc|= (2+3)/(3+5)= 0.625
p(w|c)= p(soccer|politics)= (d(w,c) + Wc)/d(c)+|Voc|= (0+3)/(3+5)= 0.375

p(w|c)= p(championship|sport)= (d(w,c) + Wc)/d(c)+|Voc|= (3+3)/(3+5)= 0.75
p(w|c)= p(championship|politics)= (d(w,c) + Wc)/d(c)+|Voc|= (0+3)/(3+5)= 0.375

p(w|c)= p(government|sport)= (d(w,c) + Wc)/d(c)+|Voc|= (1+3)/(3+5)= 0.5
p(w|c)= p(government|politics)= (d(w,c) + Wc)/d(c)+|Voc|= (2+3)/(3+5)= 0.625

p(w|c)= p(italian|sport)= (d(w,c) + Wc)/d(c)+|Voc|= (1+3)/(3+5)= 0.5
p(w|c)= p(italian|politics)= (d(w,c) + Wc)/d(c)+|Voc|= (2+3)/(3+5)= 0.625


