CLASSIFICATION (es3)

	parliament | italian | loose | win | soccer | championship | government | class				#NOTA CHE WIN E LOOSE NON DOVREBBERO PIU' ESISTERE NEL NOSTRO MODELLO ALLENATO!
d1		0	   1		1	   0      1		  1			0	    ?
d2		1	   1		0	   0	    1		  0			1	    ?

d1 classification:
p(sport|{italian , loose , soccer , championship})= p(sport)*p(italian|sport)*p(loose|sport)*p(soccer|sport)*p(championship|sport)= 0.6*0.5*0.625*0.75= 0.14
p(politics|{italian , loose , soccer , championship})= p(politics)*p(italian|politics)*p(loose|politics)*p(soccer|politics)*p(championship|politics)= 0.4*0.625*0.375*0.375= 0.04

d2 classification:
p(sport|{parliament , italian , soccer , government})= p(sport)*p(parliament|sport)*p(italian|sport)*p(soccer|sport)*p(government|sport)= 0.6*0.375*0.5*0.625*0.5= 0.036
p(politics|{parliament , italian , soccer , government})= p(politics)*p(parliament|politics)*p(italian|politics)*p(soccer|politics)*p(government|politics)= 0.4*0.625*0.625*0.375*0.625= 0.037 




